0183                                                   ; | i   @fb.topline  = Top line in FB
0184                                                   ; | i   @fb.row      = Current row in FB
0185                                                   ; |                  (offset 0..@fb.scrrows)
0186                                                   ; | i   @fb.column   = Current column in FB
0187                                                   ; | i   @fb.colsline = Columns per line FB
0188                                                   ; |
0189                                                   ; / o   @fb.current  = Updated pointer
